Example:

# printf \"
net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies = 1
\" >> /etc/sysctl.d/60-netipv4_sysctl.conf

Run the following command to set the active kernel parameters:

# {
   sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1
   sysctl -w net.ipv4.route.flush=1
}"
